flowchart TB
    C[客户端] --> GSLB[全局 DNS / GSLB]
    GSLB --> EDGE[CDN / WAF / API Gateway]

    subgraph R1[主地域 Region-1]
        direction TB
        EDGE --> LB[区域负载均衡]

        subgraph AZA[可用区 A]
            GA[Gateway A]
            SA[秒杀接入服务 A]
            QA[查询服务 A]
            CA[订单消费者 A]
            RMA[(Redis Master-1)]
            RRC[(Redis Replica-3)]
            NSA[NameServer / Controller A]
            BRA[(Broker Replica Group A)]
            PGA[(PostgreSQL Primary)]
            OTA[OTel Collector A]
        end

        subgraph AZB[可用区 B]
            GB[Gateway B]
            SB[秒杀接入服务 B]
            QB[查询服务 B]
            CB[订单消费者 B]
            RMB[(Redis Master-2)]
            RRA[(Redis Replica-1)]
            NSB[NameServer / Controller B]
            BRB[(Broker Replica Group B)]
            PGB[(PostgreSQL Sync Standby B)]
            OTB[OTel Collector B]
        end

        subgraph AZC[可用区 C]
            GC[Gateway C]
            SC[秒杀接入服务 C]
            QC[查询服务 C]
            CC[订单消费者 C]
            RMC[(Redis Master-3)]
            RRB[(Redis Replica-2)]
            NSC[NameServer / Controller C]
            BRC[(Broker Replica Group C)]
            PGC[(PostgreSQL Sync Candidate C)]
            OTC[OTel Collector C]
        end

        LB --> GA
        LB --> GB
        LB --> GC
        GA --> SA
        GB --> SB
        GC --> SC

        SA --> RMA
        SB --> RMB
        SC --> RMC

        SA --> BRA
        SB --> BRB
        SC --> BRC

        BRA --> CA
        BRB --> CB
        BRC --> CC

        CA --> PGA
        CB --> PGA
        CC --> PGA

        PGA -.同步 WAL，ANY 1.-> PGB
        PGA -.同步 WAL，ANY 1.-> PGC

        SA -.Telemetry.-> OTA
        SB -.Telemetry.-> OTB
        SC -.Telemetry.-> OTC
    end

    subgraph R2[灾备地域 Region-2]
        PGDR[(PostgreSQL 异步灾备)]
        BK[(跨地域不可变备份)]
        DRAPP[预部署或冷启动应用集群]
    end

    PGA -.异步 WAL.-> PGDR
    PGA --> BK
    RMA --> BK
    RMB --> BK
    RMC --> BK
